<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>CLEAR – Carbon Leadership</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      color: #1a1a1a;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    header {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 80px 20px 40px;
      background-color: #f5f7fa;
    }
    header h1 {
      font-size: 48px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      letter-spacing: -1px;
    }
    header p {
      font-size: 18px;
      color: #555;
    }
    .section {
      max-width: 1000px;
      margin: 40px auto;
      padding: 0 20px;
    }
    .grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
      gap: 24px;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
    .box {
      background: #f0f4f8;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 20px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
    }
    .box h3 {
      margin-top: 0;
      color: #2c3e50;
    }
    .stats {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 20px;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
    .stat {
      flex: 1 1 220px;
      background: #eaf1f8;
      border-radius: 6px;
      padding: 15px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .stat h4 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 22px;
      color: #1a1a1a;
    }
    .stat p {
      margin: 5px 0 0;
      color: #555;
    }
    footer {
      background-color: #f5f7fa;
      padding: 40px 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    footer p {
      margin: 8px 0;
    }
    a {
      color: #0070f3;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
  <h1>CLEAR</h1>
  <p>Carbon Leadership for Emissions Abatement and Removal</p>
</header>

<section class="section">
  <div class="grid">
    <div class="box">
      <h3>Mission</h3>
      <p>Catalyze carbon removal at scale by aggregating demand, validating innovation, and building digital infrastructure for MRV and procurement.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="box">
      <h3>Vision</h3>
      <p>Position the GCC as a global leader in carbon removal by leveraging its natural assets, tech capabilities, and policy ambition.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="box">
      <h3>Approach</h3>
      <p>Advance market commitments, verified carbon credit registry, and a regional innovation sandbox for scalable CDR solutions.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <h2 style="text-align:center;">Platform Highlights</h2>
  <

<div class="stat">
      <h4>$100M+</h4>
      <p>Offtake interest under validation</p>
    </div>
    <div class="stat">
      <h4>5+ Institutions</h4>
      <p>Involved in GCC MRV consortium</p>
    </div>
    <div class="stat">
      <h4>3+ CDR Tech Pilots</h4>
      <p>DAC, brine alkalinity, mineralization</p>
    </div>
    <div class="stat">
      <h4>2040 Goal</h4>
      <p>Net carbon-negative GCC region</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<footer>
  <h2>Get Involved</h2>
  <p>Email: <a href="mailto:hello@clearcarbon.ai">hello@clearcarbon.ai</a></p>
  <p>Website: <a href="https://clearcarbon.ai">clearcarbon.ai</a></p>
  <p>© 2025 CLEAR Initiative</p>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
